Freddie Jones https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freddie_Jones 0 Frederick Charles Jones (born 12 September 1927) is a retired English character actor. He is most recently known for playing Sandy Thomas in Emmerdale from 2005 until 2018. Frederick_Charles_Jones ( born 12_September_1927 ) is a_retired_English_character_actor . He is most_recently known for playing Sandy_Thomas in Emmerdale from 2005 until 2018 .
